  "form": "任意団体 internal cross-domain system-of-systems leverage substrate (NOT 一般社団 / NPO / 公益財団 / 宗教法人 法人格 — Preamble §0.4 Lv7+ unanimity lock)",
  "leverageInvariant": "L = C·(V/D)·(1+B)·(1−open), computed ON READ (edge-primary; ADR-2605312345); the 要 = argmax L. There is no :kaname/score-of-entity ground datom (N1/G4). Bridge-load is a bounded proxy for inter-layer betweenness (full multiplex betweenness = R1, labelled honestly).",
  "routeInvariant": "G2 STRUCTURAL — the route enum {open, route-around, add-redundancy, decentralize, insufficient-evidence} has no capture/seize/control/monopolize member; methods/route.cljc assert-route! RAISES on any concentration-increasing intent. The 要 is dissolved, never acquired.",
  "personExclusion": "G1 STRUCTURAL — the 要 is a structural position. methods/osekkai.cljc assert-not-person! RAISES on :person/private or a coordinate; only public ROLE nodes (:sos/role) are addressable. No per-person target is representable.",
  "noServerKey": "kaname PROPOSES (advisory:true, sent:false, server-key:false); ossekai CARRIES. No platform-held signing key (ADR-2605231525).",
  "selfCertifyingDid": "did:key:z6Mkie7K8RSVuosk5hTSphBj39ZqVqNAa1khv46BcfTJ9CKB",
  "didKeyMaterial": "Ed25519. The 32-byte seed (private key) is stored ONLY in 1Password (vault Private, item 'etzhayyim-kaname-did', field private-key-ed25519-seed-hex, CONCEALED) — NEVER committed (CLAUDE.md secrets rule). Generated 2026-06-17 (ADR-2606015600 self-certifying did:key pattern). The PUBLIC did:key above is kaname's identity + the value of KANAME_KOTOBA_OPERATOR_DID for the live kotoba bridge. Retrieve for an operator run: `export KANAME_KOTOBA_OPERATOR_DID=$(op item get etzhayyim-kaname-did --fields label=did)`. Authenticating to the node additionally requires the node to recognize this DID as an authorized operator (node-config / member-delegation step).",
  "dataModelInvariant": "kotoba Datom log (EAVT, ADR-2605262130 / 2605312345); GROUND op :add durable, DERIVED op :derived leverage integrals computed on read, never persisted as ground.",
  "crossActor": {
    "joins": "chie / tsumugi / keizu / kabuto / shiori / abaki / shionome / busshi / hokorobi / kosatsu / inochi — their DISCLOSED per-domain concentration is the input multilayer graph (live join G7/Council-gated)",
    "junkan": "ADR-2605290927 — the system-dynamics/CLD view of the same question; complementary, NOT conflated (graph-centrality vs. system-dynamics)",
